item.title: CVE-2020-12775|2024-08-04T12:04:22.894Z -- hicos -- citizen%20certificate%20client-side%20component
item.description: Hicos citizen certificate client-side component does not filter special characters for command parameters in specific web URLs. An unauthenticated remote attacker can exploit this vulnerability to perform command injection attack to execute arbitrary system command, disrupt system or terminate service.
